<paragraph id="E24D1F6CDAA5FF3E3AAAFE48998FFDD5" blockId="178.[151,1437,222,571]" pageId="178" pageNumber="179">
DISTRIBUTION 
<collectionCode id="84E387A9DAA5FF3E3B59FE489DB3FE45" box="[356,417,403,427]" pageId="178" pageNumber="179">AND</collectionCode>
HABITAT. Red Sea, East and 
<collectingCountry id="9AE55FFCDAA5FF3E3939FE499F8AFE45" box="[772,920,402,427]" name="South Africa" pageId="178" pageNumber="179">South Africa</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="9AE55FFCDAA5FF3E3998FE49983EFE45" box="[933,1068,402,427]" name="Madagascar" pageId="178" pageNumber="179">Madagascar</collectingCountry>
and western Mascarenes east to Tuamotu Archipelago, north to southern 
<collectingCountry id="9AE55FFCDAA5FF3E385DFE6C9EB1FE20" box="[608,675,439,462]" name="Japan" pageId="178" pageNumber="179">Japan</collectingCountry>
, south to Western 
<collectingCountry id="9AE55FFCDAA5FF3E394DFE6D9FC8FE21" box="[880,986,438,463]" name="Australia" pageId="178" pageNumber="179">Australia</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="9AE55FFCDAA5FF3E39D8FE6C9887FE21" box="[997,1173,438,463]" name="New Caledonia" pageId="178" pageNumber="179">New Caledonia</collectingCountry>
, and 
<collectingCountry id="9AE55FFCDAA5FF3E3EF2FE6C990BFE21" box="[1231,1305,439,463]" name="Tonga" pageId="178" pageNumber="179">Tonga</collectingCountry>
. Introduced into West Atlantic waters off Florida, 
<collectingCountry id="9AE55FFCDAA5FF3E386CFE009E9FFE1D" box="[593,653,475,499]" name="United States of America" pageId="178" pageNumber="179">USA</collectingCountry>
. Found in shallow protected coastal waters to deep, somewhat silty habitats; juveniles occur singly or in small groups among inner sheltered lagoons while adults move out to open waters over sandy areas of deep lagoons, channels, and seaward coral reefs, 
<quantity id="250AB289DAA5FF3E39DBFDF8982FFDD4" box="[998,1085,547,571]" metricMagnitude="1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.55" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="0.1" pageId="178" pageNumber="179" unit="m" value="15.5" valueMax="30.0" valueMin="1.0">
1– 
<specimenCount id="F4F4D4E5DAA5FF3E39C2FDF8982FFDD4" box="[1023,1085,547,571]" pageId="178" pageNumber="179" type="generic">30 m</specimenCount>
</quantity>
. Transitional water and marine.
</paragraph>
