<emphasis id="D086C37EDAA5FF3E3B8AFD559E56FD49" bold="true" box="[439,580,654,679]" pageId="178" pageNumber="179">New record</emphasis>
from Madang, based on specimens photographed at St. CTR 
<number id="543A0D4BDAA5FF3E3F3CFD55990DFD49" box="[1281,1311,654,679]" pageId="178" pageNumber="179" value="16.0">16</number>
